+    a) KB severity taxonomy authorship — draft from existing `/quality-check` domains as starting point, or hand-author from scratch?
+    b) Confidence math weights — equal 0.25 each, or weight `citation_rate` highest since it's the F3 guard?
+
+    ## Constraints
+    - Follow IDD: `intent.yaml` is source of truth, `SKILL.md` is compiled artifact
+    - Play L1 ≤2 agents, L2 ≤5 agents (domain); utility agents exempt
+    - Standards hierarchy KB → LTM → STM, paths from config only
